&nbsp;The premier of Free State Ace Magashule has sent condolences to Bloemfontein Celtic honorary lifetime president Petrus Molemela and his family following the passing of his wife Mme Mamorwesi.Mme Mamorwesi died on Tuesday.Magashule described her as a lovable, caring and a dedicated human being who took care of the community and its children at large.The chairman of celtics Max Tshabalala through the clubs website said the passing of Mme Molemela affected him saying he was part of the family for years and she brought them up without asking for anything in return. Show original messageThe couple were married for 61 years and had a passion for community building, sports development and a reputable spirit of enterprise.sipho jack